<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="icon", href="./images/favicon-32x32.png", type="image/png")
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="./css/main.css")
    title Frontend Mentor | Article preview component

  body(class="min-vh-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between align-items-center pt-4")
    main(class="my-auto w-75 container rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white")
      div(class="row")
        div(class="col-md p-0 overflow-hidden bg-image")
        
        div(class="col d-flex flex-column justify-content-start mt-3")
          h1(class="article-title") Shift the overall look and feel by adding these wonderful touches to furniture in your home

          p(class="my-3") Ever been in a room and felt like something was missing? Perhaps it felt slightly bare and uninviting. Iâ€™ve got some simple tips to help you make any room feel complete.

          div(class="row justify-content-between align-items-center flex-nowrap mt-auto" id="person-area")
            //- person area
            div(class="col-auto p-3 person-component")
              img(src="./images/avatar-michelle.jpg", alt="Michelle photo showing her face", class="avatar-image rounded-circle")

            div(class="col-auto p-3 mr-auto person-component")
              p(class="my-0 person-name-text") Michelle Appleton
              p(class="my-0 date-text") 28 Jun 2020

            //- share area
            div(class="col-auto p-3 share-component d-none"): p(class="my-0 share-text") SHARE

            div(class="col-auto p-3 mr-auto share-component d-none")
              a(href="#" class="mx-2"): i(class="fa fa-facebook-square")
              a(href="#" class="mx-2"): i(class="fa fa-twitter")
              a(href="#" class="mx-2"): i(class="fa fa-pinterest")

            //- share button
            div(class="col-auto p-3")
              button(type="button" class="border-0 rounded-circle share-button" id="share-button"): i(class="fa fa-share")

    footer(class="attribution my-2")
      small(class="d-block my-1 text-center") Challenge by 
        a(href="https://www.frontendmentor.io?ref=challenge" target="_blank") Frontend Mentor
        | .
       
      small(class="d-block my-1 text-center") Coded by 
        a(href="#") Jonathan Cantor
        | .

    //- jquery only for bootstrap
    script(src="./js/jquery.min.js")
    script(src="./js/popper.min.js")
    script(src="./js/bootstrap.min.js")
    script(src="./js/index.js")